GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
SESSION 2025
S 1
SENATE BILL 255
Short Title: Greenville Bulkhead Appropriation. (Public)
Sponsors: Senator Smith (Primary Sponsor).
Referred to: Rules and Operations of the Senate
March 11, 2025
1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO APPROPRIATE FUNDS TO THE CITY OF GREENVILLE FOR A
3 REPLACEMENT BULKHEAD.
4 The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
5 SECTION 1. There is appropriated from the General Fund to the City of Greenville
6 the nonrecurring sum of five million dollars ($5,000,000) for the 2025-2026 fiscal year to be
7 used to replace the existing bulkhead in the Town Common park to alleviate flooding issues and
8 deteriorating structural stability and to improve resiliency to flood events.
9 SECTION 2. This act becomes effective July 1, 2025.
*S255-v-1*

